![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/847f6e28-8e4f-4a88-ab23-48e15ba63d51/20050.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_Bronson Reed def. Roman Reigns after an accidental spear from Jey Uso through a table._**
    

Bronson Reed is the first person to pin Roman Reigns since Cody Rhodes

Bronson Reed has now pinned both Roman Reigns and Kazuchika Okada. Two of the most dominant wrestlers of the past decade.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8628e1ca-b1dc-405f-913c-29b1b8c3c8e6/20054.jpg?format=original)

Roman is furious. He specifically asked the Usos not to come out and they cost him this match.

"What did I tell y'all?? The whole world thinks I can't do shit on my own! This only works if you win!

I love you. I don't wanna see y'all till Christmas."

Roman leaves and then Jey Uso decides he doesn't want to deal with Roman anymore either.

"He always doing him! I'm outta here!"

