*   ## **_John Cena def. AJ Styles with a Tombstone Piledriver and FU_**
    

Alica Taylor delivers an emotional message to AJ Styles from John Cena

"Ladies & Gentleman, the definition of Total Non-stop Action.

The ace and undisputed boss of The Bullet Club, it's our honour as fans and my honour as an opponent to see if he can beat up John Cena one final time.

He is the face that runs the place, The Phenomenal, AJ Styles!"

John Cena and AJ Styles tore the fuckin house down one final time.

Once in a lifetime performance that saw both men pay tribute to their entire time in professional wrestling.

Go out of your way to watch this match.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/16d0318e-a895-4ec6-9eb7-ad019a85ebd7/20100.jpg?format=original)

Every tribute move performed by John Cena and AJ Styles

Cena:

Skull Crushing Finale - The Miz

The Accolade - Rusev

Walls of Jericho - Chris Jericho

Sister Abigail - Bray Wyatt

2nd Rope DDT & RKO - Randy Orton

Chokeslam - Kane / The Undertaker

Tombstone Piledriver - Kane / The Undertaker

Attempted 619 - Rey Mysterio

Attempted Pedigree - HHH

Styles:

Scorpion Death Drop - Sting

Coquina Clutch - Samoa Joe

Angels Wings - Chirstopher Daniels

Dead Eye - Frankie Kazarian

Sweet Chin Music - Shawn Michaels

